1 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Louisiana Senate does hereby commend
2 the members of the Louisiana Athletic Trainers Association for their outstanding
3 achievements, does hereby recognize and record for posterity their unwavering commitment
4 to excellence in service to the citizens of the state; does hereby extend enduring appreciation
5 for the pride and honor they bring to Louisiana, and does hereby designate March 24, 2026,
6 as Louisiana Athletic Trainers Association Day at the Louisiana State Capitol.
7 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to the
8 president of the Louisiana Athletic Trainers Association.
